ReturnPolicy.Description:
Returns / Concerns:

All items qualify for returns up to 14 days after your item is received.
If you return your purchase, these rules must be followed.
Shortages or Damages:  We strongly recommend that all Items be fully and carefully inspected at time of delivery. If there are any problems with your order, please notify me within 24 hours of delivery. Replacements are sent out upon receipt of damaged product.
Defective/damaged Returns must be received within 14 days of invoice date. Replacement will be shipped to you.
Non Defective/damaged Returns: The original purchaser has a period of 14 days from date of delivery to return any purchase for a refund, less 15% restocking fee and shipping, provided the merchandise is in new, resalable condition and returned in the original, undamaged packaging. All items must be returned in original manufacturer’s packaging, all parts, access, and paperwork. No used merchandise will be accepted.
Unless the merchandise is shipped in error, customer is responsible for outgoing freight as well as return freight. The cost of the shipping will be deducted from the credit, which the customer is entitled to upon receipt and inspection of the returned item(s). Acceptance of merchandise is final only after inspection. All warranty books, instructions manuals, parts and accessories must be included as well as the original box in which the item was shipped. To protect the original factory carton from any additional shipping damage, please place it inside another carton for return shipping.
Please note that you are responsible for the safe return of merchandise and for all shipping costs. Shipping charges are non-refundable unless the return is the result of our error. For your protection, returned packages must be insured for the value of your merchandise.

Return processing time generally takes a few weeks.
All items are IN STOCK at time of listing. 
Inventory changes constantly and it is impossible to maintain perfectly accurate count of all items.  Please do not penalize us if we have to issue you a refund!.
You must contact me to process the return with the supplier.
